title: Hypno Slave v.1.03
description: Poster: http://ipic.su/img/img7/fs/1.1534833161.jpg Description: Hello guys! We apologize for that fact that we have not post any fresh news about our project for a long time. We spent all of our free time to bring the release date. It was not easy to make quality project spending only free time on it. We worked all the time after work, all weekend and holiday. And we did it! We would like to present you first beta version of our project. In fact the game has near 40 adult scenes (including animation), more than 100 improvements, such as bodymodes and upgrades to the "servant". And interesting enemies that stand in your way during the game. And that is not all - we are planning to make regularly updates for you - adding new scenes, new improvements, new enemies, with the balancing and improving gameplay. Time between updates will depend from our supports. If we will have full time job, then we will updating our project more often. And we will create new. We are very thankful, if you send a screenshot of any bugs or strange behavior of our game here: Note: First betta of game now available on patreon. You always can leave any wishes here or on our post. We will consider all your ideas and wishes, about game process. Especially an interesting text story. We are very thankful for your patience and supports. It was most influence on us, because we are work tirelessly all free time on pure enthusiasm. That's all. Thank you for your time. Happy new year!
